Hello everyone!

Here is my context to ensure that the default system message is always CallAroundAdvisor.

Below is an example of how it turned out.

```
class DefaultSystemMessageChatAdvisor(
    private val systemPrompt: Resource,
) : CallAroundAdvisor {
    override fun aroundCall(
        advisedRequest: AdvisedRequest,
        chain: CallAroundAdvisorChain,
    ): AdvisedResponse {
        val systemMessage = SystemPromptTemplate(systemPrompt)
            .createMessage(advisedRequest.systemParams)

        advisedRequest.messages
            .addFirst(systemMessage)

        return chain.nextAroundCall(advisedRequest)
    }

    override fun getName(): String = this.javaClass::getSimpleName.toString()

    override fun getOrder(): Int = -2147482649
}
```
